{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775882120998,"sessionID":"ses_2853012c3ffeCKRazIanJjdzkh","part":{"id":"prt_d7ad2aa79001CVzZVjVX4IEo4x","messageID":"msg_d7ad2949f001uYiFBn54BxDOM0","sessionID":"ses_2853012c3ffeCKRazIanJjdzkh","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_functions.read:17","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","limit":50},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # Proposal: CLI Binary Entry Points\n2: \n3: ## AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n4: \n5: | Field | Value |\n6: |-------|-------|\n7: | **Module** | `cmd` |\n8: | **Language** | Go |\n9: | **Size** | M (Medium) |\n10: | **Status** | Proposed |\n11: \n12: ---\n13: \n14: ## Purpose\n15: \n16: Implement the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components. Each binary provides a standalone executable that initializes its respective service with proper configuration, dependency wiring, and graceful shutdown handling. This proposal delivers:\n17: \n18: 1. **agentd** — Idle cleanup controller binary that runs the Sandbox reconciler\n19: 2. **router** — HTTP session routing proxy with Gin framework\n20: 3. **workload-manager** — Sandbox orchestration controller with Kubernetes CRD management\n21: 4. **picod** — Sandbox daemon for code execution inside sandbox pods\n22: \n23: These binaries serve as the deployment targets for the AgentCube platform, enabling independent scaling, deployment, and lifecycle management of each component.\n24: \n25: ---\n26: \n27: ## Scope\n28: \n29: ### In Scope\n30: \n31: | Item | Detail |\n32: |------|--------|\n33: | **Binary Entry Points** | 4 `main.go` files under `cmd/`: `agentd`, `router`, `workload-manager`, `picod` |\n34: | **Flag Parsing** | Standard Go `flag` package with `--help` support |\n35: | **Configuration** | CLI flags for service-specific settings (ports, timeouts, Kubernetes config) |\n36: | **Graceful Shutdown** | SIGINT/SIGTERM handling with configurable timeout |\n37: | **Dependency Wiring** | Initialize clients (Redis, Kubernetes, HTTP) from configuration |\n38: | **Service Startup** | Start controllers, HTTP servers, and reconcilers |\n39: | **Health Checks** | Basic liveness/readiness endpoints where applicable |\n40: | **Logging** | Structured startup logging with version and configuration |\n41: \n42: ### Out of Scope\n43: \n44: - Configuration file support (YAML/JSON config files)\n45: - Hot configuration reloading\n46: - Service discovery integration (Consul, etcd)\n47: - Metrics and monitoring endpoints (Prometheus)\n48: - Distributed tracing (Jaeger, Zipkin)\n49: - Circuit breaker patterns\n50: - Multi-instance leader election\n\n(Showing lines 1-50 of 615. Use offset=51 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# Proposal: CLI Binary Entry Points\n\n## AR-019 — CLI 二进制入口 (4 binaries)\n\n| Field | Value |\n|-------|-------|\n| **Module** | `cmd` |\n| **Language** | Go |\n| **Size** | M (Medium) |\n| **Status** | Proposed |\n\n---\n\n## Purpose\n\nImplement the CLI binary entry points for the 4 core AgentCube components. Each binary provides a standalone executable that initializes its respective service with proper configuration, dependency wiring, and graceful shutdown handling. This proposal delivers:\n\n1. **agentd** — Idle cleanup controller binary that runs the Sandbox reconciler\n2. **router** — HTTP session routing proxy with Gin framework\n3. **workload-manager** — Sandbox orchestration controller with Kubernetes CRD management","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/proposal.md","time":{"start":1775882120987,"end":1775882120996}}}}
